Comedian Debo Adedayo, popularly known as Mr Macaroni, has said he has no hate whatsoever in his heart. The #EndSARS campaign, in a post on Twitter, revealed how a government official asked him why he holds hate for a person, which he(Mr Macaroni) failed to mention. The comedian said, “I was at an event day before yesterday, a top government worker walks up to me and asks why I hate “someone” ~ I can’t mention name. “I have no hate whatsoever in my heart. “I just want a better life for every Nigerian. “I don’t hate anyone. We all can do better.” Copyright PUNCH. All rights reserved. This material, and other digital content on this website, may not be reproduced, published, broadcast, rewritten or redistributed in whole or in part without prior express written permission from PUNCH. Contact: theeditor@punchng.com